 Edipuglia, 1989)\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/9CT5ZWIK",{"type":174,"bibl":175},"discussion",[19],{"editor":177,"principal":180,"contributors":181,"change":201},{"_":178,"ref":179},"Jonathan Prag","#JP",{"_":178,"ref":179},[182,185,189,193,197],{"_":178,"xml:id":183,"ref":184},"JP","http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537",{"_":186,"xml:id":187,"ref":188},"Marta Fogagnolo","martaf","https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163",{"_":190,"xml:id":191,"ref":192},"James Cummings","JCu","http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728",{"_":194,"xml:id":195,"ref":196},"Alex Antoniou","AA","http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703",{"_":198,"xml:id":199,"ref":200},"Simona Stoyanova","SS","https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569",{"_":202,"when":203,"who":204},"Marta Fogagnolo revised the text encoding, added dimensions, the Italian translation and commentary","2022-12-22","#martaf",{"n":98,"url":99,"height":100,"width":101,"desc":102,"surfaceType":103},[207],{"atLeast":208,"atMost":209},18,28,[211,212,213,214],"Bulletin épigraphique, 1888-","Korhonen, 2004, IMusCatania","Notizie degli scavi di antichità, 1876-","Wessel, 1989, IGCVO",[216,217,218,219],"77P5MNIR","2EUC82DH","4MCP2PVV","9CT5ZWIK",[221,222,223,21,26,30,224,225,226,227,225,228,229,123],"isic003281","epitaph for bassos",{"_":5},"catina","catania","sicilia","sicily","museo civico di catania","ancient greek",[],{"title":232,"body":233,"divs":234,"editions":261,"images":271,"handnote":277},"ISic003281. Epitaph for Bassos","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\">Ἐνθάδε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"κεῖτε\">κεῖτε\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">Βάσσος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἰατρός\">ἰατρός\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ἔζησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ν´ ☧ \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησεν\">ἐτελεύτησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">τῇ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">πρὸ\u003C/span> ιε´ ⁚ \u003Cspan data-text=\"Καλανδῶν\">Κα(λανδῶν)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Μαρτίων\">Μαρ(τίων)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"κεῖτε\">ΚΕΙΤΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">ΒΑΣΣΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἰατρός\">ΙΑΤΡΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>Ν☧\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησεν\">ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">ΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">ΠΡΟ\u003C/span>ΙΕ:\u003Cspan data-text=\"Καλανδῶν\">ΚΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Μαρτίων\">ΜΑΡ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003281_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003281_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003281.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003281-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Here lies Bassos the doctor. He lived for 50 years, and died 15 days before the Kalends of March.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Qui giace Bassos il medico. Visse 50 anni e morì 15 giorni prima delle Calende di marzo.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph presents the traditional expression \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται\u003C/span> (for the phonetic development of \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κεῖται\u003C/span> into \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κεῖτε\u003C/span> from the 3rd cent. AD, see in Catania IG 14.532 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001351\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001351\u003C/a>, Libertini (1930) 44 no.7 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001629\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001629\u003C/a>), followed by the name of the deceased, the age and the date of death (in this case expressed with the verb \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω\u003C/span> in the aorist form), which is frequent in Christian epitaphs. In this case, there is the mention (rare in Christian epitaphs) of the profession of the deceased, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἰατρός\u003C/span>. For other Sicilian inscriptions mentioning doctors, see Rizzo, F. P. (1989), \"La menzione del lavoro nelle epigrafi della Sicilia antica: Per una storia della mentalità\", pp.62-64 and Manganaro, G. (1994), \"Iscrizioni, epigrafi ed epigrammi in Greco della Sicilia orientale di epoca romana\", in \"Mélanges de l’École Francaise de Rome: Antiquité\" 106(1), 79–118, at p.107.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1920 p.432 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 140 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Orsi NSA 1918 63 no.7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzo 1989 64 no.25 \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 171 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>A with straight bar (l. 2) and slanting bar (l. 1, l. 5), squared Ε and Σ, ligature between Π and Ρ at l. 6. Double dot at l. 6.\u003C/p> Lines 1-6  18-28  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[235,238,241,244,247,249,252,255,258],{"id":236,"html":237},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\">Ἐνθάδε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"κεῖτε\">κεῖτε\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">Βάσσος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἰατρός\">ἰατρός\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ἔζησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ν´ ☧ \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησεν\">ἐτελεύτησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">τῇ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">πρὸ\u003C/span> ιε´ ⁚ \u003Cspan data-text=\"Καλανδῶν\">Κα(λανδῶν)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Μαρτίων\">Μαρ(τίων)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"κεῖτε\">ΚΕΙΤΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βάσσος\">ΒΑΣΣΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἰατρός\">ΙΑΤΡΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>Ν☧\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐτελεύτησεν\">ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">ΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">ΠΡΟ\u003C/span>ΙΕ:\u003Cspan data-text=\"Καλανδῶν\">ΚΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Μαρτίων\">ΜΑΡ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":239,"html":240},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003281_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003281_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003281.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003281-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":242,"html":243},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":245,"html":246},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Here lies Bassos the doctor. He lived for 50 years, and died 15 days before the Kalends of March.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":245,"html":248},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Qui giace Bassos il medico. Visse 50 anni e morì 15 giorni prima delle Calende di marzo.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":250,"html":251},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph presents the traditional expression \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται\u003C/span> (for the phonetic development of \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κεῖται\u003C/span> into \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κεῖτε\u003C/span> from the 3rd cent. AD, see in Catania IG 14.532 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001351\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001351\u003C/a>, Libertini (1930) 44 no.7 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001629\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001629\u003C/a>), followed by the name of the deceased, the age and the date of death (in this case expressed with the verb \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω\u003C/span> in the aorist form), which is frequent in Christian epitaphs. In this case, there is the mention (rare in Christian epitaphs) of the profession of the deceased, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἰατρός\u003C/span>. For other Sicilian inscriptions mentioning doctors, see Rizzo, F. P. (1989), \"La menzione del lavoro nelle epigrafi della Sicilia antica: Per una storia della mentalità\", pp.62-64 and Manganaro, G. (1994), \"Iscrizioni, epigrafi ed epigrammi in Greco della Sicilia orientale di epoca romana\", in \"Mélanges de l’École Francaise de Rome: Antiquité\" 106(1), 79–118, at p.107.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":253,"html":254},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1920 p.432 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 140 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Orsi NSA 1918 63 no.7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzo 1989 64 no.25 \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 171 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":256,"html":257},"handnote","\u003Cp>A with straight bar (l. 2) and slanting bar (l. 1, l. 5), squared Ε and Σ, ligature between Π and Ρ at l. 6. Double dot at l. 6.\u003C/p> Lines 1-6  18-28  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":259,"html":260},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[262,264,267,268],{"html":263},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":265,"lang":123,"html":266},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\">Ἐνθάδε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"κεῖτε\">κεῖτε\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr